        public Collection<String> keySet()
        Description copied from interface: Properties.Source
        Returns all keys, for which Properties.Source.get(String) does not return null. This operation is optional - if this source does not support this operation, it returns null. The result is always unmodifiable.
        Specified by:

      • reload

        public PrefixSource reload()
        Description copied from interface: Properties.Source
        Reloads the contents of this source from its origin, if this makes sense for the implementation. The reloaded contents are returned as a new source - this source is not modified.

        If the implementation does not support reloading, simply return this, which is also the default implementation.

        Specified by:
        reload in interface Properties.Source
